AB  - This note is a follow-up on two earlier studies—the first published in 1989 and the second in 1991. A sample of tenured entrepreneurship scholars, with significant track records in publishing, rated key management journals with respect to their appropriateness as outlets for scholarly research in the entrepreneurship field. The results of the survey are reported.
