T1  - Measuring the performance of emerging businesses: A validation study
AU  - Chandler, Gaylen N.
AU  - Hanks, Steven H.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 8
IS  - 5
SP  - 391
EP  - 408
PY  - 1993
DA  - 1993/09/01/
